highlights.text: “Padam Kadala” by Sagar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hyderabad, up 55 spots at #25.
“Almost Padipoyindhe Pilla (From "Das Ka Dhamki")” by Leon James, Adithya RK, and Poornachari has been on Top Songs Hyderabad the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Sid Sriram has the most spots on Top Songs Hyderabad. “Urike Urike” is the highest at #4.
“Kanula Chatu Meghama” by Kalyani Malik, Aabhas Joshi, and Lipsika is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hyderabad at #33.
